title: 이달의소녀탐구 #62 (LOONA TV #62)
summary:
0:02 --HaSeul mentions how this is YeoJin’s first foreign trip and that she has to take care
of her being the oldest member. (MomSeul 💚)
0:10 -- YeoJin has a photoshoot and HaSeul teaches her how to pose. YeoJin looks
awkward as this is her first ever photoshoot.
0:27 -- PD asks HaSeul what she thinks about YeoJin’s photoshoot. HaSeul mentions
that YeoJin still has to learn a lot from her and looks at her like a coach.
